    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i've taken it before and i was fine. it's just a mild headache, not like a major thing. would a single dose really do anything to my kidneys if it's just once in a while? i'm just trying to avoid waiting for an appointment if it's not a big deal.",
