      "content": "i understand, but my doctor is super busy and i really hate the throbbing in my head right now. if i just take a standard dose like 200mg and maybe drink a bunch of water, isn't that enough to keep it safe? it's just one pill, it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle. can't i just do that once?",
